{
  "stem": "8191.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a wedding in the rabbi's house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now you also had a young son, when, when did he-- when did he show up?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Claude showed up the 27th of May, 1942.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not later. 1939. '39.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Claude was born July 27, 1929-- 1939.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Six weeks before the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had to join my regiment four days after the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went to, to my regiment, and, and two weeks later the-- it quieted down.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The shock was over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Go home.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I went home till February.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] February I was called back to the, to the army.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they assigned me to the Polish, new Polish army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] In, in that time, and this is late February, 1940.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] In the end of May, my regiment received an order.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They have to move.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So there was a train waiting for us, they put us in a train.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And for two or three days, from close to the border of Germany, close to the Maginot line.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was two or three days till we came to a place we didn't know what it is, or where it is even.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And directly from the train, aboard ship.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the ship was already backed, already, I think.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we went way.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Eight days later, I woke up in the morning, and I find myself in the water.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And in the water was like a fire, all around.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's all that I remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I woke up, when I find myself aboard the ship.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, where they going?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't know where I am, even.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said they going to London, to England.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
